Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, clear the way, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't obstruct our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, at least tell us how the police are viewing this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you considering this case \N as part of the serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've heard that the murdered Jopp \N couple did not have any children either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the circumstances here match those throughout Germany \N of the serial middle-aged couple homicides perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've also heard that the BKA \N investigator in charge of the serial murders is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then this {\i1}is{\i0} related to the serial homicides?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it would be better to \N ask that BKA investigator directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to get a better story than the other papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save a nice big space for the headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kipper, from the Hamburg Tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the investigator from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a connection between this murder \N and the serial homicides of middle ages couples--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kipper, from the Hamburg Tag...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you, and only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case is one of the serial homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the suspect is the Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just read the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been executed in an identical \N manner to all of the other murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the special exclusive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hamburg Tag is a major \N newspaper around here, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, your story will \N circulate among other major newspapers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:29.18,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,196)\pos(317,315)}Runge's Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I have become the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it would be better not to make the Jopps suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what a friendly couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am invited in without a hassle \N and they show me the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't suspect anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the husband's chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I sit in the guest chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The husband dies over there \N on the floor, several minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have not made my move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she is not in this room yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be getting tea ready in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea will not be served.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wife was stabbed from the back inside the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means I must begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take out my knife and stab at the startled husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who quickly attempts to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The husband runs away from an injury on his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next attempt gets his right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screw up again!  What an amateur I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The husband is screaming for his wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she doesn't hear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wife had become hard of hearing lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream!  Yell and cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can take care of the wife after I finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the husband's left hand print.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've cornered the husband in front of this sideboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't finish the husband off here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's five meters from here to the \N floor where the husband finally dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I finish him off here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man killed the Jopps?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's not necessarily the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just asking a favor of the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to greet and treat this \N man normally when he appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, call me as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no danger involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's terrible that such a thing \N happened in a quiet residential neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jopps were so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Jopp would always greet me cheerfully \N whenever I called out to her in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you called out to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her hearing has been poor for about a year now, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was written by her doctor in her patient records.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably barely heard your greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Mrs. Jopp, she must have \N sensed my presence and greeted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The neighbors weren't aware of her hearing difficulties?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is quite a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extraordinary feat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be doing so well at your age, Mr. Ziebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's only because the car manufacturer we \N contracted with happened to do very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry for the loss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of your aunt and uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were the only real family I had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't have any children,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they must have loved their nephew very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like a real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hope you catch the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're almost positive of his identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's that former Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are well informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!  There were \N similar incidents like this in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will you be inheriting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm just curious since the Jopps were very wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the sole beneficiary of their will,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you implying?  This is not the time for such talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is often the case, when a company appears
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be doing very well on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is actually in dire straits on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like I did it, for the inheritance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went out to dinner with your \N secretary and employees after a business meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you even have witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Runge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking into that nephew these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His company appears to be in good standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but their stock investments have failed, \N so internally, they're in quite a predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, look at your actions... \N You are thoroughly investigating his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the real story here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly believe that this case
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is connected to the serial \N homicides involving middle aged couples?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of our exclusive story, \N the other papers are going along with that theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it has nothing to do with the serial murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then our story would be a total mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the work of a copycat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One done to make it look like the serial homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to change the article immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that this case is one of the serial \N middle aged couple homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I write a lie like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I may not look like it, but I'm still a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use to trying to intimidate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kipper, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite an enticing woman, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you have a warm household
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a lovely wife and daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with such an enticing woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame you for being unfaithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it would be better if you wrote a \N special on it, with regard to the serial homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will surely come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a few questions I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have been a wonderful couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did they ever have a foster child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they ever live with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it was only for a short amount of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were quite fond of their nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you like another cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it; it's the man from the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's at my house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Runge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is someone here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Jopps' nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I did it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that I killed them for inheritance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I owe some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money they left me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will probably save me from this crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I am not that kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just for that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You treat me like a criminal, and this is what I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be going somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take back the \N disrespectful comments you made the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man the police had following you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police here have deemed you innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who do you think is the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could care less about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I manage to capture that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there is blood over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He screwed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that this murder was committed by that Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it is a copycat case of the \N serial middle aged couple homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something in this case \N that wasn't found in all of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer cornered the victim here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, he didn't finish him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it was farther away, all the way over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenes of the crimes committed by the man I am after
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are made to seem like a robbery,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no emotion can be detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in this particular crime scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is an overwhelming amount of emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer became flustered, just because he \N saw his face and that of the victim's in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police here are incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing more than
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the work of a copycat who tried to imitate Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is this going to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching for you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to have a nice, long chat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use running now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sit down and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to continue this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed the Jopps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn myself in, just don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he's going to bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do this to Detective Runge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only leave him in front of the hospital and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you regained consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the key to these cuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find your gun there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just checked your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, the knife didn't penetrate the abdominal cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you are bleeding too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't stop the bleeding, you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confess,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder of the three men, \N including the director, at Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the murders of the middle-aged \N couples during these past three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confess that it was all your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are really going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's all Johan's doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm looking for Johan, the real killer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is you, yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to find anything of \N much use in the abandoned warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I did find enough for first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I just need these hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my hands were free, I could save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Dr. Tenma, you're an excellent doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You play the virtuous man without a single fault, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many have you killed with those hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to become Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is the virtuous man going to \N transform into the heartless murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are becoming delusional due to the loss of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your crime scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your crime scenes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you lose emotion when \N you handle people's lives every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That calm is always there in the crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In every surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wondered, "Am I going to make a mistake?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can I pull it through?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will problems spontaneously arise?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really terrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my hands...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I stay calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,move...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will... shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your pants pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look better than you do when you are at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for causing concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the first aid was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said that you wouldn't be alive \N now if it hadn't been for the prompt treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I owe Tenma my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even though Tenma got away,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ziebel confessed to killing the Jopps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Runge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Runge had his life saved by Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may affect his ability to arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should remove him from the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for taking good care of Detective Runge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you are quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a very nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him that he didn't have to start rehab so early,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's already begun working with the \N squeeze ball and walking in the hallways.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but he says he's having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he says it often.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That there is nothing more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was his name, that criminal..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says it's most fun to go after a criminal like Tenma.
